description:

Bella Rossi made it to the Semi finals of Last Season ( season 9). Mistress Kara is a rookie for this year but she has been taking down everyone who has crossed her path, including last season's Summer Vengeance 2nd place taker( 2nd place is first loser), Izamar.
Will Mistress Kara make Bella bow down to "the Queen" or will Bella Annihilate-her.
An outstanding standing 69 lift and carry with blow job and pussy licking in round 4 .
title: Awesome Welter Weight Match up with Mistress Kara vs. Bella Rossi
